#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:5
msgid "Hook Modifier"
msgstr "钩挂修改器"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:7
msgid ""
"The Hook Modifier is used to deform a *Mesh*, *Curve* a *Lattice* using another object (usually "
"an *Empty* or a *Bone* but it can be any object)."
msgstr "挂钩修改器用其他物体（通常是 *空物体* 或 *骨骼*，但可以用任何物体）来对变形*网格*、*弯曲**晶格*。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:10
msgid ""
"As the hook moves, it pulls vertices from the mesh with it. You can think of it as animated :doc:"
"`proportional editing </editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/proportional_edit>`."
msgstr "当钩子移动时，它从它与网格拉扯顶点。你可以把看作添加了动画的 :doc:`衰减编辑 </editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/proportional_edit>`。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:14
msgid ""
"While hooks do not give you the fine control over vertices movement that shape keys do, they "
"have the advantage that you can grab vertices directly for manipulation."
msgstr "在顶点运动方面，虽然挂钩操作不能提供像形变键一样好的可控性，但是它有着可以直接抓取顶点操作的优势。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:20
msgid "Empty used as Hooks to deform a subdivided cube."
msgstr "用空物体做为挂钩来使细分的立方体变形."

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:24
msgid "Options"
msgstr "选项"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:28
msgid "Hook Modifier."
msgstr "钩挂修改器。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:30
msgid "Object"
msgstr "物体"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:31
msgid "The name of the object to hook vertices to."
msgstr "挂钩顶点的物体的名字"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:34
msgid "Vertex Group"
msgstr "顶点组"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:33
msgid "Allows you to define the influence per vertex."
msgstr "允许你按顶点设定影响."

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:35
msgid "Useful when you do not something other than a spherical field of influence."
msgstr "除了球形影响区域之外没有其他东西时很有用."

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:36
msgid "Radius"
msgstr "半径"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:37
msgid "The size of the hooks influence."
msgstr "挂钩作用的范围"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:40
msgid "Strength"
msgstr "强度"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:39
msgid ""
"Adjust this hooks influence on the vertices, were (0.0 to 1.0) (no change to fully follows the "
"hook)."
msgstr "调整挂钩对顶点的影响,范围在(0.0到1.0)(不改变完全跟随的挂钩)."

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:41
msgid ""
"Since multiple hooks can work on the same vertices, you can weight the influence of a hook using "
"this property."
msgstr "由于多个挂钩操作可作用在同一个顶点上，你可以用这个属性来加权一个挂钩操作的影响力。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:43
msgid "Falloff Type"
msgstr "衰减类型"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:43
msgid ""
"This can be used to adjust the kind of curve that the hook has on the mesh. You can also define "
"a custom curve to get a much higher level of control."
msgstr "该项可以用来调节在网格上牵引修改器用到的曲线，你也可以自定义曲线获取更高级别的控制度。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:49
msgid "Uniform Falloff"
msgstr "均匀衰减"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:46
msgid ""
"This setting is useful when using hooks on scaled objects, especially in cases where non-uniform "
"scale would stretch the result of the hook."
msgstr "当你在缩放过的物体上用牵引修改器时，该项设置有用，尤其是在非均匀缩放会挂钩牵引修改器作用的结果的场合中。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:49
msgid "This is especially useful for lattices, where its common to use non-uniform scaling."
msgstr "该项对晶格非常有用，在使用非均匀缩放里很常见。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:51
msgid "The following settings are only available in Edit Mode:"
msgstr "以下设置仅在编辑模式可用："

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:53
msgid "Reset"
msgstr "重置"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:54
msgid "Recalculate and clear the offset transform of hook."
msgstr "重新计算，并清除挂钩操作的偏移变换"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:56
msgid "Recenter"
msgstr "重新指定中心"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:56
msgid "Set hook center to the 3D cursor position."
msgstr "设置挂钩中心为3D光标的位置。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:58
msgid "Select"
msgstr "选择"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:59
msgid "Select the vertices affected by this hook."
msgstr "选择受该挂钩影响的顶点"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:61
msgid "Assign"
msgstr "指定"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:61
msgid "Assigns selected vertices to this hook."
msgstr "指定选择好的顶点到该挂钩修改器。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:65
msgid ""
"The Hook Modifier stores vertex indices from the original mesh to determine what to affect; this "
"means that modifiers that generate geometry, like a Subdivision Surface Modifier, should always "
"be applied **after** the Hook Modifier; otherwise the generated geometry will be left out of the "
"hook's influence."
msgstr "挂钩修改器保存了来自原始网格的顶点索引以确定影响哪些顶点；这意味着，产生新的几何形状的修改器（例如细分修改器），应该在挂钩修改器 **之后** 应用；否则产生的几何形状将不会受挂钩操作的影响。"
